    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into a time capsule of automotive elegance. This isn't just a car; it's a preserved legacy, a mechanical masterpiece that hums with the quiet confidence of a well-kept secret. Every curve of its silhouette catches the light like polished marble, and the interior welcomes you with the scent of heritage and luxury. Driving this vehicle feels like stepping into a private sanctuary where the world outside fades into a blur of motion and grace. It\u2019s more than mere transport\u2014it\u2019s an heirloom waiting for its next curator to appreciate its soulful purr and unrivaled presence.",
      "price": 46500.0,
